title: SPAMfighter Free 5.8.0
description:
Spam Filter for Outlook and Express, Windows Mail and Servers

SPAMfighter is Europe&#039;s leading spam filter developer, providing spam protection across the globe for 3.874.977 home and business users on PC&#039;s and Servers.


3.874.977 users are already spam free with SPAMfighter, and in the last 24 hours 4.799 new SPAMfighters joined the battle. If a SPAMfighter receives a spam mail that is not detected by SPAMfighter, the user reports the spam mail with one click, and it&#039;s removed from the rest of the SPAMfighter community in seconds.
